name: GoodMeme

description.en: GoodMeme is a community driven project based on producing, celebrating and expanding the use of memes. It wants to create a Platform that brings together all the communities for the simple love of memes. It plans to reward community members for the creation of memes over a prolonged period of time, it also wants to encourage members of different coins and different spaces to all come together to create something we can all enjoy!
